  "3137560": {
    "name": "The Liminal Dimension",
    "steam_appid": 3137560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/d6a88b74214a381852735e89979d12cc.avif?t=1769787860\" width=636 height=107 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在《The Liminal Dimension》的不安、超现实世界中——一款心理恐怖游戏，将测试你感知的极限。在这个世界里，没有愉快的鸭子或色彩缤纷的装饰；只有寂静、空虚和无尽的循环，带来更多的循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/812fd8761719766f79ca0c99efba8713.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/812fd8761719766f79ca0c99efba8713.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/812fd8761719766f79ca0c99efba8713.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你唯一的目标是找到逃脱的路径，但请小心——每个转弯、每条走廊都可能看起来令人不安地熟悉。这是似曾相识，还是更为邪恶的东西？每一个决定、每一步，都将你拉近解决方案……或更深地陷入这个噩梦般的维度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Liminal Dimension》汲取了最新恐怖游戏的趋势，其中边界模糊的空间成为我们最深层恐惧的舞台。在你探索这些空间时，你将经历到迷失方向、混乱，甚至是令人恐惧的平静。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/e9ffdcdaa8ba90001a36138fc39c4983.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/e9ffdcdaa8ba90001a36138fc39c4983.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/e9ffdcdaa8ba90001a36138fc39c4983.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极具氛围：</strong> 跨越现实与梦境边缘的边界空间，创造出身临其境且阴森的环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>似曾相识效果：</strong> 每个循环略有不同，但又奇异地熟悉，增加了不安感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>线性但不可预测的玩法：</strong> 穿越迷宫，在过去和现在之间的界限模糊，让你怀疑什么才是真实的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖：</strong> 恐惧不是来自追逐怪物或突如其来的尖叫——但你确定吗？在《The Liminal Dimension》中，你永远无法确定你所害怕的恐怖是否只是存在于你的内心中。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会找到出路，还是永远迷失在《The Liminal Dimension》中？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/acba5a32597daec47f952eedb95a9546.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/acba5a32597daec47f952eedb95a9546.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/acba5a32597daec47f952eedb95a9546.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>立即将游戏添加到你的愿望单中，别错过这个独特的恐怖体验发售。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/381b12446bad570b575d7b11b59efa3a.poster.avif?t=1769787860\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/381b12446bad570b575d7b11b59efa3a.webm?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137560/extras/381b12446bad570b575d7b11b59efa3a.mp4?t=1769787860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
